{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-jsx","path":"/css-position/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Web Like Spider"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e02cee79-e644-5c86-9d7b-7e11ed5de52b","excerpt":"The CSS position property is one of the fundamental properties you need to know in order to feel\ntruly comfortable in your CSS knowledge. So before you start…","html":"<p>The CSS position property is one of the fundamental properties you need to know in order to feel\ntruly comfortable in your CSS knowledge. So before you start digging deep into CSS do yourself a favor\nand learn it. Don’t worry though, it’s really rather simple.</p>\n<h2 id=\"values\" style=\"position:relative;\">Values</h2>\n<p>There are 5 possible values of the position property:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#static\">static</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#relative\">relative</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#absolute\">absolute</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#fixed\">fixed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sticky\">sticky</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>These five position values change how the <strong>top</strong>, <strong>bottom</strong>, <strong>left</strong> and <strong>right</strong> properties affect the element.\n(With the exception of static which is not affected.)</p>\n<h2 id=\"static\" style=\"position:relative;\">static</h2>\n<p>This is the default position value, all elements have a position of static unless you have specified otherwise.</p>\n<p>Elements with <code class=\"language-text\">position: static;</code> are not positioned in any special way and simply follows the normal flow of the webpage. Top, bottom, left and right will not affect elements with a position value of static.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> static<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-left: 0; max-width: 450px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web-like-spider/static/18a3dda8bd8580eca1dfc587f74fd15d/21b4d/position_static.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83185840707964%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Position sticky\"\n        title=\"Position sticky\"\n        src=\"/web-like-spider/static/18a3dda8bd8580eca1dfc587f74fd15d/fc2a6/position_static.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web-like-spider/static/18a3dda8bd8580eca1dfc587f74fd15d/2519b/position_static.png 113w,\n/web-like-spider/static/18a3dda8bd8580eca1dfc587f74fd15d/3684f/position_static.png 225w,\n/web-like-spider/static/18a3dda8bd8580eca1dfc587f74fd15d/fc2a6/position_static.png 450w,\n/web-like-spider/static/18a3dda8bd8580eca1dfc587f74fd15d/23296/position_static.png 675w,\n/web-like-spider/static/18a3dda8bd8580eca1dfc587f74fd15d/1cfc2/position_static.png 900w,\n/web-like-spider/static/18a3dda8bd8580eca1dfc587f74fd15d/21b4d/position_static.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"relative\" style=\"position:relative;\">relative</h2>\n<p>Elements with relative positioning are positioned relative to their normal(static) position.\nTop, bottom, left and right moves the element away from this position.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>This will adds 20 pixels to the top of the elements original position and\n50 pixels to left.</p>\n<p>This positions the element 20 pixels from the top and 50 pixels to the left of the elements original position.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-left: 0; max-width: 450px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web-like-spider/static/70390a27bf351bb67bc03729d55dcd6a/21b4d/position_relative.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83185840707964%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Position relative\"\n        title=\"Position relative\"\n        src=\"/web-like-spider/static/70390a27bf351bb67bc03729d55dcd6a/fc2a6/position_relative.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web-like-spider/static/70390a27bf351bb67bc03729d55dcd6a/2519b/position_relative.png 113w,\n/web-like-spider/static/70390a27bf351bb67bc03729d55dcd6a/3684f/position_relative.png 225w,\n/web-like-spider/static/70390a27bf351bb67bc03729d55dcd6a/fc2a6/position_relative.png 450w,\n/web-like-spider/static/70390a27bf351bb67bc03729d55dcd6a/23296/position_relative.png 675w,\n/web-like-spider/static/70390a27bf351bb67bc03729d55dcd6a/1cfc2/position_relative.png 900w,\n/web-like-spider/static/70390a27bf351bb67bc03729d55dcd6a/21b4d/position_relative.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"absolute\" style=\"position:relative;\">absolute</h2>\n<p>The position of an element with <code class=\"language-text\">position: absolute;</code> is based on its nearest <strong>positioned</strong> parent i.e. the nearest\nwrapping element with a position other than static.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">bottom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 15px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>This will position our element 10 pixels from the bottom and 15 pixels from the left of our <strong>positioned parent</strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-left: 0; max-width: 450px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web-like-spider/static/31d7085c401ffc86f24892829fecb509/21b4d/position_absolute.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83185840707964%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Position absolute\"\n        title=\"Position absolute\"\n        src=\"/web-like-spider/static/31d7085c401ffc86f24892829fecb509/fc2a6/position_absolute.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web-like-spider/static/31d7085c401ffc86f24892829fecb509/2519b/position_absolute.png 113w,\n/web-like-spider/static/31d7085c401ffc86f24892829fecb509/3684f/position_absolute.png 225w,\n/web-like-spider/static/31d7085c401ffc86f24892829fecb509/fc2a6/position_absolute.png 450w,\n/web-like-spider/static/31d7085c401ffc86f24892829fecb509/23296/position_absolute.png 675w,\n/web-like-spider/static/31d7085c401ffc86f24892829fecb509/1cfc2/position_absolute.png 900w,\n/web-like-spider/static/31d7085c401ffc86f24892829fecb509/21b4d/position_absolute.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>Do note</strong> that absolute(and fixed) elements are removed from the normal document flow. Meaning it wont affect any other\nelements, they will behave as if there is no other element there. Our element may therefore end up on top of another.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-left: 0; max-width: 450px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web-like-spider/static/7c98ccd8762e6cf81e35d1ff38e9a1b0/21b4d/position_absolute_covering.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83185840707964%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Position absolute covering\"\n        title=\"Position absolute covering\"\n        src=\"/web-like-spider/static/7c98ccd8762e6cf81e35d1ff38e9a1b0/fc2a6/position_absolute_covering.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web-like-spider/static/7c98ccd8762e6cf81e35d1ff38e9a1b0/2519b/position_absolute_covering.png 113w,\n/web-like-spider/static/7c98ccd8762e6cf81e35d1ff38e9a1b0/3684f/position_absolute_covering.png 225w,\n/web-like-spider/static/7c98ccd8762e6cf81e35d1ff38e9a1b0/fc2a6/position_absolute_covering.png 450w,\n/web-like-spider/static/7c98ccd8762e6cf81e35d1ff38e9a1b0/23296/position_absolute_covering.png 675w,\n/web-like-spider/static/7c98ccd8762e6cf81e35d1ff38e9a1b0/1cfc2/position_absolute_covering.png 900w,\n/web-like-spider/static/7c98ccd8762e6cf81e35d1ff38e9a1b0/21b4d/position_absolute_covering.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>This unsuspecting element has been partially covered by our box.</p>\n<h2 id=\"fixed\" style=\"position:relative;\">fixed</h2>\n<p>Fixed elements are always positioned relative to the document i.e. the browser window. Which means they are are\nalso not affected by scrolling.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fixed<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>This positions the element 100 pixels from the left and 30 pixels from the top of the window, no matter how far down the page you scroll.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-left: 0; max-width: 450px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web-like-spider/static/0015f036c1e3457bd176825506f1a426/21b4d/position_fixed.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83185840707964%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Position fixed\"\n        title=\"Position fixed\"\n        src=\"/web-like-spider/static/0015f036c1e3457bd176825506f1a426/fc2a6/position_fixed.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web-like-spider/static/0015f036c1e3457bd176825506f1a426/2519b/position_fixed.png 113w,\n/web-like-spider/static/0015f036c1e3457bd176825506f1a426/3684f/position_fixed.png 225w,\n/web-like-spider/static/0015f036c1e3457bd176825506f1a426/fc2a6/position_fixed.png 450w,\n/web-like-spider/static/0015f036c1e3457bd176825506f1a426/23296/position_fixed.png 675w,\n/web-like-spider/static/0015f036c1e3457bd176825506f1a426/1cfc2/position_fixed.png 900w,\n/web-like-spider/static/0015f036c1e3457bd176825506f1a426/21b4d/position_fixed.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Like with <code class=\"language-text\">position: absolute;</code> fixed elements are removed from the document flow. See <a href=\"#absolute\">absolute</a>.\nThis makes fixed elements useful for popups and modals.</p>\n<h2 id=\"sticky\" style=\"position:relative;\">sticky</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">position: sticky;</code> is a bit of a bonus and has limited albeit powerful use cases.\nA sticky element behaves as if it is relative-positioned until it reaches a specified point, where it starts\nbehaving as if it’s fixed-positioned.</p>\n<p>Lets showcase this with an <strong>example:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> sticky<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Try scrolling the window below and notice how the <code class=\"language-text\">.box</code> element behaves.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://codesandbox.io/api/v1/sandboxes/define?embed=1&_MyUpgoZUBBwwlYlwzKidMDqOcmzy9grQExgSUmxgwBZFS5ikMuSWL0-TI2je2nNqhvIX7pgl2EYEu6iaztQl3Lwnx0if8pHgiwZX3N4KsKDoXO0MDtM6VzKugQ5Ds8qClqulD5HQBDavazpLlcUD4sI6bCJQYCQDa9iYK4OYOiaUIimosZ1HmsxVqk1w4GykychA3KXgKQE0WEErUNKsryoqnEqjaGjPJqaFCjAuq9jAhrGqa5qWnUqA2oi6AYQ2THX